{"tid":1290890,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【用 10 分鐘照顧自己】瞓得唔好，無晒胃口快啲入嚟！！","createTime":"2019-07-06T16:00:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T15:23:15.000Z","uid":86509,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2b4de08bc9302a486f784c6fd6f5b758138a6ba4","tid":1290890,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T16:00:23.000Z","msg":"【用 10 分鐘照顧自己】<br />\n<br />\n我哋可能成個月都瞓得唔好，無晒胃口<br />\n可能好緊張，好難過<br />\n但我哋可以用10分鐘好好呼吸<br />\n我哋可以好好照顧自己<br />\n再繼續好好咁<br />\n一齊行落去<br />\n<br />\n一班熱愛香港嘅創作人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/2203415499933439/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F2203415499933439%2F&d=Yo3BLZp%2B9L0ow7gqQKw5zVgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=ee5a81a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/2203415499933439/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以上轉至：立場新聞<br />\n<br />\n休息係為未來行更遠嘅路<br />\n休息夠，頭腦先清晰<br />\n休息夠，先有力打仗<br />\n而家就同我休息<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dff64ec2e4d9582a3d4a51cada22a42649b2676","tid":1290890,"uid":86509,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T16:02:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20160614/photo/bkn-20160614221231400-0614_00862_001_03p.jpg?20160615010018\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20160614%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20160614221231400-0614_00862_001_03p.jpg%3F20160615010018&h=84507970&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"834273f9a9ae10741f91ab02dcf9db066c9e1778","tid":1290890,"uid":86509,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T16:11:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/kVru4cH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%